---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" sideBarActiveItemID="about">
  <div>
    <div class=" text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5">Who am I?</div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-4">
    I am a passionate software developer with a strong background in web development and a keen interest in learning new technologies. Over the years, I have worked on various projects that have helped me hone my skills in front-end and back-end development.
  </p>
  <img src="/profile.webp" alt="Profile image" class="mt-4 rounded-lg" />
  <p class="mt-4">
    My journey in the tech world started with a curiosity for how things work on the internet. This curiosity quickly turned into a passion, leading me to pursue a career in software development. I enjoy solving complex problems and building efficient, scalable solutions.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-4">
    When I'm not coding, I love to read about the latest trends in technology, contribute to open-source projects, and participate in tech communities. I believe in continuous learning and strive to improve my skills every day.
  </p>

</BaseLayout>
